short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Gathers trend data for your Google searches

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Search trends is a tool that allows you to see location search data in real time using data from Google trends. The tool allows you to hover over a map to see search trends in the past year, see related queries, and provides realistic data for marketers looking to grow their business.
